Hey Streamlitters,&#x1f44b;=20
=20
Let's start things off by celebrating a huge recent milestone: There are no=
w over 1 million of you building with Streamlit each month! =09 &#129327; T=
he idea of this many devs seemed like a lofty dream just a few years ago, b=
ut you made it possible. THANK YOU for building, contributing, sharing, and=
 growing this awesome community of Streamlitters!=C2=A0=E2=9D=A4=EF=B8=8F

And there's so much more to come. Read more <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyL=
VJGTy0yMjcAAAGgpd2C5LjyEV-gW6wnBOmLbG8lh1Z0QABQE6IFAUx3SAQtYw7njijDuonzMmin=
Gw_AoCPCFjU=3D> about the journey and see what=E2=80=99s ahead =E2=80=94inc=
luding=20
agent skills, greater extensibility, and even more powerful dashboards.
Beyond the big celebration, there are two new releases to explore, a refres=
hed components gallery to browse, and some exciting events to put on your c=
alendar!
&#128680; =C2=A0Release 1.55
The latest release introduces new ways to manage app state and user interac=
tion. Here are some highlights:=20



=09- &#127871; Introducing dynamic containers: st.tabs, st.popover, and st.=
expander can rerun the app when they are opened or closed by setting the on=
_change parameter. If a key is also provided, you can programmatically open=
 and close them, too
=09- &#128391; Announcing widget binding! Most non-trigger widgets have a b=
ind parameter to simplify syncing widget state with query parameters
=09- =09 &#128279; st.image has a link parameter to make images clickable w=
ith HTTP/HTTPS URLs
=09- &#129399; st.Page has a visibility parameter that lets you hide pages =
in the navigation menu while keeping them routable
Release 1.54=20

Version 1.54 brought even more UI flexibility to your toolkit:



=09- =09&#127912; You can use custom theme colors in simple chart elements
=09- &#129399; Widgets now use key-based identity to prevent unwanted reset=
s
=09- &#128512;=09 st.logo now supports Material icons and emojis
=09- &#127384; New client.showErrorLinks to configure display of error help=
 links
See the full changelog <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGgpd2C5K=
K06qMcBgy3tvhkhpRn3oppCpm99uJ0D8pAW9ACwG9iO8w1gS0djZ0Dzen6XM-XI9k=3D> for m=
ore info and all updates!
&#x1F5BC; New components gallery
The community components gallery is a great resource for finding ways to ex=
tend Streamlit, and it just got a major upgrade! You can now find the right=
 tools in seconds with a cleaner layout and improved search + sorting. Want=
 to contribute your own component? Add it to the new open-source registry w=
ith a simple PR. Learn more <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGgp=
d2C5Td46bwm-OkqgFJ9z8ZgdBLLk6u2ina91tTIwPbpETopYzF2-eJmDWzRWrCElohE4o4=3D>.
&#128198;=C2=A0Upcoming events
Come say hi to the team at these upcoming events!




=09- April 30: Streamlit virtual meetup <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGT=
y0yMjcAAAGgpd2C5KAFbfOIkTiD1p1tPUa8--dkZUdPqHPMETbgeQiZxGt6JMvY5nW8Cwjep-Fg=
90LnrK8=3D>, Global (stay tuned for more details)
=09- May 13=E2=80=9319: PyCon US <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcA=
AAGgpd2C5K7j3mgY1SCAHXHlkQPJSQ9pA70ysatPMFeknDjGAWU5PDnlBXLsEYel-bkVH5BsLOU=
=3D>, Long Beach, CA
=09- June 1=E2=80=934: Snowflake Summit <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGT=
y0yMjcAAAGgpd2C5EbqFrFUQOrirN1vAHNkSuATaoC6XXBPxeZCCnb3p7YT_JVdQM7Rge9zZbQf=
1djCUN0=3D>, San Francisco, CA



Join your local meetup group <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGg=
pd2C5K7klMwDI6jITTlx4ByioiQeXsPLbhGPnxUZ_uiKhBMYE3i0OhtKB5pjWI6mhul2EtM=3D>=
 to stay up to date on activities in your city and let us know <https://go.=
snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGgpd2C5OzAMmHkyinjKaQNRVbitScqYvLtbgh1W1NYJ=
50VlhHACCu3MzCCEU4vxERwW3wQ-Zc=3D> if you=E2=80=99d like to help host a mee=
tup.
&#10024;=C2=A0Community showcase
Explore new apps, components, and tutorials from the community:=20




=09- Get started with Streamlit Agent Skills <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUy=
LVJGTy0yMjcAAAGgpd2C5CsA1E8V2EYZaJejP2xaqisPYIF9Vn6sblC008Fy62DzXgE8QLwiBG5=
vsmIPe54zyWU=3D> with Ayumu=E2=80=99s guide.
=09- Learn 25+ Streamlit tricks from a co-founder dashboard <https://go.sno=
wflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0yMjcAAAGgpd2C5VOtWJb9PgPlklcH4z7Tt0-aY9TtpetlTZsXruvH=
CYX7ALoaKxbcz-dC1nDXUyvAJ7c=3D> in Fanilo=E2=80=99s overview.
=09- Create custom components from scratch <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLV=
