=09- Hear two AI models debate a topic <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy=
0yMjcAAAGgpd2C5QHU-ZJHZutlTrk1uOcEofz9FBxsDL2uQSZJqEZ5qzcoWuKH91C19djLowWFP=
wsCcyQ=3D> using Siddhant=E2=80=99s app.
See more in the=C2=A0monthly roundups <https://go.snowflake.net/MjUyLVJGTy0=
yMjcAAAGgpd2C5Lx8BPp8o9_0nBMMkpGiXDrsPVBoy5m4D_tPl-cATNRIeN7RFJ4Ta0E3cG7Ahr=
DiGno=3D>. &#129395;

To show off your creations, don=E2=80=99t forget to tag @Streamlit on socia=
l.
